Axxess has launched a new promotion which offers fibre-to-the-home users who transfer their line to them a two-month subscription for only R2. “Transfer your fibre line to Axxess before 31 July 2019 and only pay R2 for 2 months,” the ISP said in a promotional mail. Users will be billed R1 on signup, R0 on activation and R1 on the first “renewal” month. Axxess will also cover the R999 connection fee associated with transfers. To qualify for the Axxess fibre transfer promotion, users will need to: The promotion is only available to existing Openserve and Vumatel subscribers.